{"tid":448694,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人翻工全日都唔會傾計，日日自己食飯","createTime":"2017-10-26T12:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T15:19:33.000Z","uid":129959,"like":82,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"83a2e780298491e41ed1ccb943aa1687eb04efcb","tid":448694,"uid":129959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:30:11.000Z","msg":"基本上除咗同上司講工作上嘅嘢，或者同vendor傾嘢<br />\n基本上全日唔會同同事傾計，一齊食飯就更加唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工作上溝通無問題，但係唔識同人職場上small talk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我唔怕獨處，不過驚人覺得我係怪人/好串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f4f5526d2dc15c0b5a9051436d7e0fb68fcb11","tid":448694,"uid":118493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:31:46.000Z","msg":"我啲同事唔會傾計，日日帶飯係自己位食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d63118f8082b8237f5f444b872fbd3d93a72fe5","tid":448694,"uid":129959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:34:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我啲同事唔會傾計，日日帶飯係自己位食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成間department/公司氣氛都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係調翻轉，大部分後生仔/外向撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618255e03c78e5e518736f7e1d99afd90da85d49","tid":448694,"uid":112071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:40:46.000Z","msg":"成個team 都無乜偈傾，但明明全部都幾後生<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">返工好痛苦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af2cb06e93f50c732695c54240a0d8d1438ee28","tid":448694,"uid":129959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a80124c021b5221e3ee123c0d57c1064acea4f","tid":448694,"uid":30694,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T03:46:03.000Z","msg":"以前成日講野唔會停，但係返工之後就少左好多野講，變到沉默寡言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工根本講多錯多，唔知人地咩底就亂講實奶野，如果講得多其他人以為你地fd又會搵人搞鳩你，所以唔出聲做隱形人算鳩數，起碼唔會煩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb6d6d528dceee01d1c2aee363d6fe195f9bb02","tid":448694,"uid":33539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:05:49.000Z","msg":"唔同人SOCIAL比人話你異類呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5590cc5f24f51248f3abce310de046b26a87a09","tid":448694,"uid":129142,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:42:35.000Z","msg":"我就調番轉頭 本來個人鍾意一個人食飯 但因為細公司 少同事 佢哋傾向一齊食<br />\n為咗唔做怪人 要迫自己融入<br />\n但其實各自搞手機 無咩嘢傾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35ecf45c140f128a771c61b0112a746b95e3058","tid":448694,"uid":3647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:45:51.000Z","msg":"我番工無野做就係係全程自己一個"},{"pid":"5ec723b75ac9511dc18e74e94645163089b572ec","tid":448694,"uid":56657,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前成日講野唔會停，但係返工之後就少左好多野講，變到沉默寡言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工根本講多錯多，唔知人地咩底就亂講實奶野，如果講得多其他人以為你地fd又會搵人搞鳩你，所以唔出聲做隱形人算鳩數，起碼唔會煩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一樣，出去同班fd好多野講<br />\n偏偏係公司就唔想出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a955c15a880e64d338f0feb5eb163bcdc001be","tid":448694,"uid":46124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:04:12.000Z","msg":"Same here<br />\n覺得自己就屈死<br />\n淨係同上司講工作上嘅嘢 同其他同事無機會交流<br />\n今日我就翻夠一個月 仲係咁悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ded800c55df15defdede9b217838d20e7ee6a8","tid":448694,"uid":46124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我啲同事唔會傾計，日日帶飯係自己位食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成間department/公司氣氛都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係調翻轉，大部分後生仔/外向撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n   <br />\n<br />\n我想過黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8537210965c000b92fe7ba265cedfdf0ea87f788","tid":448694,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799177ab6e6aa77003c93cc6f61b4aa48e37abe4","tid":448694,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"一個後生仔都無<br />\n傾計都有只限工作囉<br />\n放左工就自己返屋企咁<br />\n星期五搵下飯腳都無<br />\n利申: 隔離公司D囡囡個個戰鬥格返工,好想識返個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d08e722ae5c0be4a07c1023e6860dc596fefcb7","tid":448694,"uid":46124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個後生仔都無<br />\n傾計都有只限工作囉<br />\n放左工就自己返屋企咁<br />\n星期五搵下飯腳都無<br />\n利申: 隔離公司D囡囡個個戰鬥格返工,好想識返個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n  <br />\nD後生係曬隔離team<br />\n一齊做野都係啊嬸級<br />\n出黎做野係咪識個朋友都咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b272bc37e475b0da0fd5e7ae2451c96e19d4425","tid":448694,"uid":145148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:31:51.000Z","msg":"做左個幾月 都無乜講過野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成公司都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650f61bdc15bdbd9537fd130c4ce3d31d2b16837","tid":448694,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:42:26.000Z","msg":"做左一年. 冇傾過計."},{"pid":"5ba3efd5a95f7c5281bcc4703325a9e0745bc766","tid":448694,"uid":54593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:42:54.000Z","msg":"原來有咁多巴打都係咁<br />\n我之前返份工office 可以好嘈<br />\n但而家轉左新工個零月完全相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ecd78796d7e27f279df479cb2fa7afc4cc763c","tid":448694,"uid":30694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前成日講野唔會停，但係返工之後就少左好多野講，變到沉默寡言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工根本講多錯多，唔知人地咩底就亂講實奶野，如果講得多其他人以為你地fd又會搵人搞鳩你，所以唔出聲做隱形人算鳩數，起碼唔會煩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一樣，出去同班fd好多野講<br />\n偏偏係公司就唔想出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁，同fd就會啟動返個掣係咁講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都已經好少約了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8ece4d52615846062ce19e2dfb5bd4b720643a","tid":448694,"uid":46124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:29:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前成日講野唔會停，但係返工之後就少左好多野講，變到沉默寡言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工根本講多錯多，唔知人地咩底就亂講實奶野，如果講得多其他人以為你地fd又會搵人搞鳩你，所以唔出聲做隱形人算鳩數，起碼唔會煩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一樣，出去同班fd好多野講<br />\n偏偏係公司就唔想出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁，同fd就會啟動返個掣係咁講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都已經好少約了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明好想同朋友多d出黎<br />\n但唔知點解就係漸漸疏遠<br />\n結果d心情都無乜點好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae3a794ddd3b21b6bb83e98bf05206e6df80f6e","tid":448694,"uid":37682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返工姐 識朋友咩黎"},{"pid":"8dfb75a43e5573dc3d2874e032128ea296082512","tid":448694,"uid":124322,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:43:14.000Z","msg":"番工識唔到朋友架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同你fd完就有咩都推你出黎送死擋箭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1e9d5527aa17b0d1853c05fba090d2daeb0dbb","tid":448694,"uid":73058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c69cce8ecacecd5a8233304602e4112c8542c2","tid":448694,"uid":49944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返工姐 識朋友咩黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意，到時咪又係要爭上位<br />\n朋友，你做埋我個份"},{"pid":"4e9d15051efaae437ebb8ac2de15c8b4d1a962f7","tid":448694,"uid":129959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d01fcc1cd2f55e3decd9f3631d68dc978ecb68e","tid":448694,"uid":141033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T19:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前幾份工同事關係都唔錯，係𠵱家呢份工嘅風氣戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工第一日老細已經叫我唔好同同事太熟，唔好好似中學雞咁要約埋一齊食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個office 靜到仆街，個個都唔講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d4c3dfc00c7911d4a7deefb08bacd21c6294e8","tid":448694,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T19:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前幾份工同事關係都唔錯，係𠵱家呢份工嘅風氣戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工第一日老細已經叫我唔好同同事太熟，唔好好似中學雞咁要約埋一齊食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個office 靜到仆街，個個都唔講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老細驚你地互爆人工 佢會仆街"},{"pid":"47f7e190e52181771a7dec88b588946c26d7199b","tid":448694,"uid":12496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:36:12.000Z","msg":"唔埋堆就會比人杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  利申日日都一個人食"},{"pid":"3cfe9920bc8c939f25642faa2d7e761f4265fccb","tid":448694,"uid":102978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:52:38.000Z","msg":"以前份工會<br />\n因為同事問題"},{"pid":"ca0e19e5801a1732421595facd09cce6bf35e918","tid":448694,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"對住班西同事真係唔想講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要扮social應機好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n耐唔耐一個人食飯又要諗理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd0b4a7a9d4e1e800c55ffdea59ac269d198815","tid":448694,"uid":129142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對住班西同事真係唔想講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要扮social應機好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n耐唔耐一個人食飯又要諗理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 有咩高招 同病相憐 但我諗我無呢個勇氣 其實每次聽到佢地帶飯 我都好高興 因為我講明只會出去食 所以咁樣先可以一條友食到飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd7bf44c58e228f602f5d88cfc7e9b182944893","tid":448694,"uid":129142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:40:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前幾份工同事關係都唔錯，係𠵱家呢份工嘅風氣戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工第一日老細已經叫我唔好同同事太熟，唔好好似中學雞咁要約埋一齊食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個office 靜到仆街，個個都唔講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前間公司都係咁 一入嚟就叫我唔好同班同事咁close 話會影響工作表現 後尾先知間公司老細好仆街 成日拖糧 被人告 廢事我知道呢單嘢 宜間間公司應該執咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afde6d3008652e80a66fb7fd700c429e2512b740","tid":448694,"uid":23433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:43:15.000Z","msg":"我食飯都唔會想成班人食<br />\n但次次佢地問到我又唔好意思拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9152087e06e983eca15d5abcefc2a16d08a250a4","tid":448694,"uid":89917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:58:44.000Z","msg":"工作地點得2個人，<br />\n老細出街食，<br />\n我日日帶飯得自己一個食。<br />\n已經麻木。"},{"pid":"b529160af91b401648f90cebca59b266928fdcf0","tid":448694,"uid":129959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我食飯都唔會想成班人食<br />\n但次次佢地問到我又唔好意思拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你帶飯 佢地就自動自覺唔問"},{"pid":"9530e76dff79de16bfde811848a43d7e4532151a","tid":448694,"uid":23433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我食飯都唔會想成班人食<br />\n但次次佢地問到我又唔好意思拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你帶飯 佢地就自動自覺唔問</blockquote><br />\n帶飯咪又係要同人social<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想自己一個摺咋"},{"pid":"cea6e44b4c2ca1c02396e90d7737c439a6746b1b","tid":448694,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"有乜好傾"},{"pid":"e72e00be40cf9119f54404a8ba8fe1b5b9afbd8b","tid":448694,"uid":35106,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:48:14.000Z","msg":"以前岩岩出黎做野好天真地諗住同同事做到好朋友，以為好傾就一定對方鐘意自己<br />\n其實同事咪又係焗住共同做事<br />\n放工放假啲私人時間咪又各自各<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63918b73cddf6ba4dcc79a4aa6ace899a583cdeb","tid":448694,"uid":24617,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"計照傾 飯照自己一個食通常我都分開坐<br />\n唔想食飯都要戴住個面具做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2996fd7e979fc7e81ab2aea53014978978f0c711","tid":448694,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:13:07.000Z","msg":"唔係唔會傾, 係根本唔撚想傾"},{"pid":"838beef47b7ee284dd31f222c122409d838f3718","tid":448694,"uid":135463,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"返左差唔多一個月<br />\n除左工作上要溝通之外<br />\n幾乎無同過同事講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司附近無咩好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以帶飯自己食都無咩問題<br />\n最好唔好有人阻住我玩手機添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ee3e78ca6067cad5942f8fc2f8adbaaabb2e97","tid":448694,"uid":121695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:59:56.000Z","msg":"Same here"},{"pid":"27eea75d4e29900c2920fe9cffcd733e9b9f3f46","tid":448694,"uid":